{"tid":1429817,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警總爆發手足口病數警染病　衛署未接呈報 (22:06)","createTime":"2019-08-07T14:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T15:13:07.000Z","uid":40628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eecd26d7eb0ab981d305e89d58ffc8406f2088ed","tid":1429817,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:54:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190807/s00001/1565186564787/%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%A3%E7%97%85%E6%95%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85-%E8%A1%9B%E7%BD%B2%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%A5%E5%91%88%E5%A0%B1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00001%2F1565186564787%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%2591%2588%25E5%25A0%25B1&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLJvkp%2FM1ZBOvf84g0fLsyFs%3D&h=1466c3ba\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190807%2Fs00001%2F1565186564787%2F%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%2589%258B%25E8%25B6%25B3%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2595%25B8%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2597%2585-%25E8%25A1%259B%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%2591%2588%25E5%25A0%25B1&h=3faf27de\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190807/s00001/1565186564787/%E8%AD%A6%E7%B8%BD%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E6%89%8B%E8%B6%B3%E5%8F%A3%E7%97%85%E6%95%B8%E8%AD%A6%E6%9F%93%E7%97%85-%E8%A1%9B%E7%BD%B2%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%A5%E5%91%88%E5%A0%B1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n傳媒人潘小濤今早在facebook轉載警隊內部消息指出，近日警務人員長期當更，食無定時，無法上廁所，加上長期缺乏睡眠，「近排好多人病，但都唔敢攞病假，你自己病缺席，少咗人，即係令到你啲同事危險咗，不時見到同事自己攞包藥出嚟食，警察總部更加爆發手足口病，因為大家打緊仗，冇人會考慮儀態，通地瞓，通地食。衛生自然變差」。<br />\n<br />\n警方向本報確認，警察總部於7月下旬有數名警務人員確診手足口病，相關人員現正休假或已復工。為確保其他人員免受感染，管方已經按指引於相關地方進行徹底清潔和消毒。 衛生署表示，衛生防護中心暫未有接獲有關呈報。<br />\n<br />\n根據《預防及控制疾病條例》(第599章)，本港共有50種須呈報的傳染病，所有註冊醫生若發現懷疑或證實屬須呈報的傳染病，均須通知衛生防護中心，惟不包括手足口病，中心鼓勵院舍或學校通報懷疑爆發個案，以便調查及控制感染。醫學會副會長鄭志文表示，目前有指定表格供醫生填寫後交予衛生署，但通常學校會率先作出通報手足口病個案，醫生未必會重複該步驟。"},{"pid":"c14923d5a81b8464c6b3248ecea91e652e07d4c1","tid":1429817,"uid":197783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:56:28.000Z","msg":"關咩事， 去完日本返黎染病咋。"},{"pid":"d3227eba04de4cdf50ea8bdac3ae7f1dc60c8c18","tid":1429817,"uid":149833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"香港警察 污糟邋塌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病唔好睇醫生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />撤崗吖嗱"},{"pid":"e113f29b6705b28a5603b7f68244fabcc6170319","tid":1429817,"uid":152222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T15:13:07.000Z","msg":"有病記得唔好睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rXHF0dN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrXHF0dN.gif&h=391d3689&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}